data.text: Shout out to Yukon, OK!!!! I love it, most people might be like-‚Äúwhere?!‚Äù That‚Äôs where I live girl! I hope you loved your visit, the people are crazy nice here-it was one of the 1st things I noticed when we moved out here, I could stay forever!
You forgot where you just went last weekü§£
Everything is amazing in DC! We love it there!!!! If you can pop over to Georgetown it‚Äôs so lovely!!!
Anything specific you do while your pregnant and flying?

The zoo! If I remember correctly it‚Äôs free üòÅ and I heard it‚Äôs a good one. We didn‚Äôt have our daughter with us in July or we would have gone. The Segway and bike tours are amazing but with the little guy that will be challenging unless you have someone that will keep him. The top of the trump hotel has a tower that looks over the entire city, used to be a post office a very long time ago. There are tons of things to do, lots of museums and activities. Lots of great restaurants too üòÅ
I freaking LOVE DC!!! Our favorite restaurant is @busboysandpoets ! Great food, amazing atmosphere, and an awesome bookstore‚úåüèΩ
I loooooove DC. But I mostly love that you can just pop over to Maryland for all the blue crab you can eat ü§§
@megmarsh810 get up to pee/walk every hour, compression socks! And sometimes where a mask if it‚Äôs flu season üíô
All of the Smithsonian Museums are free including the zoo - the World Series is this weekend in DC so be prepared for excess crowds in some parts!!
@cmsbarro10 we have the wedding Saturday and Sunday in Rockville MD so we should miss most of that!
You went to Pagosa Springs?! That‚Äôs where we went for part of vacation last month!!
Old town Alexandria is my home‚ù§Ô∏è‚ù§Ô∏è we‚Äôre missing it terribly!
@lauraraeschaller Ben‚Äôs mom has a house there!! We were there this week, last year!!
@the_sugar_butcher we‚Äôre actually staying in Rockville MD! Seafood rec??

@brittkovacs there‚Äôs so many great places! Maryland Blue Crab House is great because you can order them by the dozen (small, med or large crabs) and Bo Brooks! But honestly blue crab is just one of those things you can‚Äôt get in California and in my opinion you can‚Äôt go wrong with any place you choose to go eat it that‚Äôs near where you‚Äôre staying! It‚Äôs the BEST CRAB.
@the_sugar_butcher so we‚Äôre an hour and 34 minutes from there.... NEXT üòÇ
@brittkovacs oh good!! Rockville is a great area :)

‚†Ä
It is just a beginning of a big journey! And Yes, Fight for your Dreams and They Will Come True!!! Fight as it is your last day on Earth!!!
